mc_cpp : A basic Monte Carlo simulations software.

----------------------------------------------
TESTED PLATFORMS AND COMPILERS:
----------------------------------------------
* Linux : - GCC-G++ 4.7 .
          - Intel icpc (ICC) 13.1.0 .

* MS Windows : - MS Visual C++ 2012 (with Visual Studio 2012 Ultimate Edition)
               - MinGW GCC-G++ 4.7 .

